{"tid":1427004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我只會係兩個情況下割席","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:03:42.000Z","uid":81046,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6adae0b43c7a06e4a4a21af71341f2746b3f537e","tid":1427004,"uid":81046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"一、行動故意傷及無辜。任何對前線手足安全有威脅既人均絕非無辜。<br />\n<br />\n二、侵害私人財產，例如搶劫途人同商鋪。<br />\n<br />\n只要對準政權同狗，任何行動我毫不猶豫地支持，都係果句，扔核蛋都唔割。<br />\n<br />\n我地必須要比市民大眾知道，佢地要驚既並非前線手足，而係黑社會同班狗。黑警會無差別攻擊任何人，包括街坊記者急救。"},{"pid":"9609a2447d2e6834447ae8be45fa81a5910af34c","tid":1427004,"uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"c35a7e4a66471df8378627a28d8d664a7d91ddbf","tid":1427004,"uid":101507,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:39:29.000Z","msg":"丟核彈都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae5a415b6dd1950bc96d2a6e19fccf7db4eeb36","tid":1427004,"uid":297236,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ce89f62c5851af32f4120802d71121b6ffb631","tid":1427004,"uid":142517,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:40:28.000Z","msg":"鍚春袋割唔割好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500da184c0c243d81a5f502258de5aacc4a9af73","tid":1427004,"uid":81046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4ae5a415b6dd1950bc96d2a6e19fccf7db4eeb36","tid":1427004,"uid":297236,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"錫岩人囉"},{"pid":"60edf21f583fc27ed4e1553b9f2309ad2e3feb77","tid":1427004,"uid":117638,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:40:48.000Z",